---
import { siteConfig } from "../config";

const coreDevelopment = [
  "HTML5",
  "CSS3",
  "JavaScript (ES6+)",
  "Node.js",
  "Express",
  "Cloudflare (Pages/Functions/D1)",
  "Git",
];

const designCollab = ["Figma", "Notion", "Discord"];

const aiEfficiency = ["ChatGPT", "Notion AI", "Midjourney", "Windsurf", "Gemini"];
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="py-16 sm:py-20 mb-20"
  style={`font-family: Pretendard, "Noto Sans KR", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;`}
>
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0B1B3A]">소개</h2>
      <div
        class="w-14 h-1 mt-3 rounded-full"
        style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
      />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-6">
        <h3 class="text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.25rem] font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1B3A] leading-tight">
          문제 앞에서는 <span class="hl" style={`--hl-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}>집요하게</span>, 팀 안에서는 <span class="hl" style={`--hl-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}>든든하게</span>.
          <br />
          끝까지 완주하는 풀스택 개발자 <span class="hl" style={`--hl-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}>이혜원</span>입니다.
        </h3>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.75] text-[#1C2B4A]">
          <p>
            웹/앱 디자인부터 프론트엔드, 백엔드, DB 설계, 배포까지 서비스 개발의 전 과정을 주도하며 폭넓은 기술적 커버리지를 갖췄습니다.
            마주한 문제는 밤을 새워서라도 해결해내고야 마는
            <span class="font-semibold" style={`color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}> 집요한 끈기(Grit)</span>가 저의 가장 큰 무기입니다.
            이러한 열정으로 캡스톤 디자인 경진대회 2위라는 성과를 증명해 냈습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            팀 프로젝트에서는 리더의 방향성을 존중하며 확실한 의견 제시로 힘을 싣는
            <span class="font-semibold" style={`color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}> 스마트한 팔로워</span>입니다.
            팀이 흔들릴 때는 멘탈을 잡아주는 중심이 되고, 동료가 기술적인 어려움을 겪을 때는 기꺼이 도맡아 해결하는
            <span class="font-semibold" style={`color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}> 기술적 멘토</span>로서,
            팀 전체가 '완주'할 수 있도록 이끄는 든든한 파트너가 되겠습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl"
                style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}12; color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M8 9l3 3l-3 3" />
                  <path d="M13 15h3" />
                  <path d="M4 4h16v16H4z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-[#0B1B3A]">Full-Stack</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Frontend UI/UX 설계부터 Serverless DB 구축까지 전 과정 주도
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl"
                style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}12; color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                  <circle cx="8.5" cy="7" r="4" />
                  <path d="M20 8v6" />
                  <path d="M23 11h-6" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-[#0B1B3A]">Leadership</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  팀 목표 달성을 위한 적극적인 소통과 리더십
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl"
                style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}12; color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M12 2l1.5 4.5L18 8l-4.5 1.5L12 14l-1.5-4.5L6 8l4.5-1.5L12 2z" />
                  <path d="M19 13l1 3l3 1l-3 1l-1 3l-1-3l-3-1l3-1l1-3z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-[#0B1B3A]">Problem Solving</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  운영 효율을 고려한 데이터 관리 시스템 및 어드민 개발
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-[#0B1B3A]">My Toolbox</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">업무에 바로 적용하는 기술과 도구들</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}12; color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}>
              <span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">💻</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#0B1B3A]">Core Development</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-600">서비스 개발의 핵심 역량</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {coreDevelopment.map((skill) => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#F7FAFF] text-[#0B1B3A] border border-gray-200 rounded-full text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">
                {skill}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}12; color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}>
              <span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">🎨</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#0B1B3A]">Design & Collab</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-600">기획과 소통을 명확하게</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {designCollab.map((tool) => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#F7FAFF] text-[#0B1B3A] border border-gray-200 rounded-full text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">
                {tool}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center" style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}12; color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}>
              <span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">🤖</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#0B1B3A]">AI Efficiency</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-600">AI로 개발 생산성 극대화</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {aiEfficiency.map((tool) => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#F7FAFF] text-[#0B1B3A] border border-gray-200 rounded-full text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">
                {tool}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hl {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 0;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .hl::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -0.08em;
    right: -0.08em;
    bottom: 0.12em;
    height: 0.42em;
    background: var(--hl-color);
    opacity: 0.28;
    border-radius: 0.28em;
    z-index: -1;
  }
</style>
